---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Paine Field Limo Service | PAE Airport Car Service | Emerald City Limos"
  description="Professional limo service to Paine Field / Snohomish County Airport (PAE) in Everett, WA. Alaska Airlines transfers, 24/7 availability, meet and greet included. Book your PAE airport car now."
  keywords="paine field limo service, PAE airport car service, everett airport transportation, snohomish county airport limo, paine field airport transfer, alaska airlines everett limo"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569154941061-e231b4725ef1?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop&q=85"
      alt="Paine Field Snohomish County Airport limo service Everett"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      width="1920"
      height="1080"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">PAE Airport</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 drop-shadow-2xl">
        Paine Field <span class="text-[#d4af37]">Limo Service</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-gray-100">
        Professional airport transfers to Snohomish County Airport in Everett, WA
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK PAINE FIELD TRANSFER
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all inline-block">
          (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Stats -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-emerald-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">24/7</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Available</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">30 mi</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">From Seattle</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">Alaska</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Airlines Hub</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#d4af37] mb-2">4.9</div>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Star Rating</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Paine Field -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Paine Field Airport Limo Service by <span class="text-emerald-700">Emerald City Limos</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Paine Field / Snohomish County Airport (PAE) in Everett, Washington offers a refreshing alternative to the crowds of Seattle-Tacoma International. Alaska Airlines operates commercial flights from Paine Field, making it a popular choice for travelers in Snohomish County, north Seattle, and the Eastside.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The terminal at Paine Field is modern, compact, and stress-free. No long walks, no massive security lines, and easy parking. For travelers flying Alaska Airlines out of Everett, it is often the preferred choice over SeaTac.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Emerald City Limos provides reliable limo service to and from Paine Field from all of Snohomish County, north King County, and the greater Seattle area. Our chauffeurs track your flight and meet you at arrivals to ensure a smooth transition from plane to vehicle.
          </p>
          <a href="/book-now" class="inline-block bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all">
            Book Your Paine Field Transfer
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Paine Field Service Features</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Flight Tracking</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Real-time Alaska Airlines flight monitoring included</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Meet and Greet</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Chauffeur waiting at arrivals with name sign</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Flat-Rate Pricing</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No surge pricing, price locked at booking</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">All Snohomish County</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Everett, Lynnwood, Edmonds, Marysville, Bothell and more</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Seattle and Eastside</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Service from all of King County to Paine Field</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg mt-0.5">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Infant Car Seats</strong>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Available at no extra charge when requested at booking</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Popular Routes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Popular Paine Field Routes</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Flat-rate limo pricing to and from Paine Field Airport</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Everett to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $69</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">5 miles, approx 10-15 minutes from downtown Everett</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Lynnwood to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $79</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">12 miles, approx 15-25 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Seattle to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $129</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">30 miles, approx 40-55 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Bellevue to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $139</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">35 miles, approx 45-60 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Kirkland to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $129</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">25 miles, approx 35-50 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Bothell to Paine Field</h3>
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">From $99</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">18 miles, approx 25-35 minutes depending on traffic</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mt-6">Prices are estimates. Get an exact quote when booking.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Paine Field -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Fly Out of Paine Field?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">The benefits of choosing PAE over SeaTac</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Faster Check-In</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Paine Field is a small terminal with shorter security lines. Arrive 60-90 minutes before your flight instead of the standard 2+ hours at SeaTac.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">📍</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Closer for North Sound</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">For travelers in Everett, Lynnwood, Edmonds, Bothell, and north Seattle, Paine Field saves 30-60 minutes versus driving to SeaTac.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">😌</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Stress-Free Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No massive crowds, easy parking, and a modern comfortable terminal. A significantly more pleasant experience than SeaTac during peak hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Paine Field Limo Service FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Which airlines fly out of Paine Field?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Alaska Airlines operates commercial flights from Paine Field (PAE) to various destinations. The airport also hosts private, charter, and cargo operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How far is Paine Field from Seattle?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Paine Field is approximately 30 miles north of downtown Seattle, typically a 40-55 minute drive depending on traffic conditions on I-5.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Paine Field limo service available 24 hours?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We provide 24/7 limo service to and from Paine Field including early morning departures and late night arrivals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you serve all of Snohomish County to Paine Field?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We pick up from all Snohomish County cities including Everett, Lynnwood, Edmonds, Marysville, Mukilteo, Mill Creek, Bothell, Mountlake Terrace, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How early should I arrive at Paine Field?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Paine Field recommends arriving 90 minutes before domestic departures. The terminal is compact so security is much faster than SeaTac. We factor in your recommended arrival time when scheduling your pickup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Book Your Paine Field Limo Today</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-200">
        Stress-free transportation to Snohomish County Airport. Serving all of the North Sound and greater Seattle area.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book-now" class="bg-[#d4af37] hover:bg-[#b8941f] text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          BOOK NOW
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12065959675" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-emerald-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all inline-block">
          Call (206) 595-9675
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
